name: Ticket to the moon
description:
Indonesian rave toad will take you to the full moon party. 
Come take a ride on his magical rocket.

This is my artistic recreation of my time in Gill Trawangan with @Allykhat328 for the Full Moon party.
All Images were created from photos taken by myself in Indonesia or digital hand drawings  by myself
Rocket and Love hearts drawn by @allykhat328
Photos edited in gimp. Digital drawing in ibis paint. All brought together in Final cut pro.
